And I don’t think she is responsible for pulling Harry away… She more than likely asked to step back on her own in a private conversation with Prince Harry and come out only when there was an event they had to do together.  She wasn’t stupid… She knew exactly who she married and the life that he was born into and what the expectations on him were. She would not have asked him to drop all of that… It’s more likely that she had to admit defeat and trying to do any independent appearances.
